    comment: '<p>You can <em>pause</em> and <em>play</em> CSS animation by changing its <code>animation-play-state</code> property.</p>\n<p>Setting it to <em>paused</em> stops your animation in place, until you change <code>animation-play-state</code> to running, for example on hover.</p>\n<pre><code class="language-css">.animating_thing {\n    animation: spin 10s linear infinite;\n    animation-play-state: paused;\n}\n.animating_thing:hover {\n    animation-play-state: running;\n}\n</code></pre>\n',
